An open source Bitcoin [[pooled mining|Pooled_Mining]] server created by puddinpop.

The clients connect through a JSON-based protocol with the [[RPC_Miner]] pooled mining clients created by puddinpop.

The distribution includes:

* remoteminer server for CPU
* remoteminer server for 4Way
* remoteminer server for ATI OpenCL GPUs
* remoteminer server for NVidia CUDA GPUs

